    <div class="content"><p>While I agree with your position on this one, it is really no<br />
surprise.  When a country uses torture to defend "freedom",<br />
how believable is it anyway?</p>
<p>There is something more attractive about an honest dictator<br />
than someone who behaves the same but claims to be defending<br />
the free world at the same time.</p>
