    <div class="content"><p>This is the clearest explanation I've yet seen of this argument, Brad...thanks. I can see (though I'd disagree with) someone DISMISSING this point, but I can't see anyone MISUNDERSTANDING it; you've nailed the point completely. Keep up the great work.</p>
